rows.label: tev001001_MSG0004
rows.name: Sorry, I was just...thinking about stuff.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1009
rows.name: Hey, any chance you want to add me to your team?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1010
rows.name:
I mean, no. Never mind. Of course you wouldn't.
...Would you?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1011
rows.name:
Really? Wow, that's great! So to be honest,
I'm a terrible fighter—but I'll work really hard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1012
rows.name:
Er, right. No. Of course not.
I don't know what I was thinking...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1017
rows.name:
I heard you're tracking some sort of unidentified
spacemen.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1018
rows.name:
Well, maybe I could help. Spaceman was my nickname
in high school, after all.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1019
rows.name:
Really? Wow, that's great! So to be honest,
I'm a terrible fighter—but I'll work really hard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1020
rows.name:
Wait, aren't you going to tell me your high school
nickname?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1027
rows.name:
If you don't want to get noticed by the tainted,
spacing out like that is a technique that always
works for me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1032
rows.name:
It terrifies me to even think about this, but...
Well, we have to save our fellow BLADEs.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1033
rows.name: So please take me with you to Oblivia.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1034
rows.name: Okay. Thanks. I'll try not to slow you down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1035
rows.name:
Okay. If you ever change your mind, I'll be ready.
Well, to the extent I'll ever be, at least.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1040
rows.name: Sylvalum is a strange land enveloped by mist.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1041
rows.name:
If you take me along, we'll have to be careful not to
get lost. But take me anyway, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1042
rows.name: Thanks. I'll try not to slow you down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1043
rows.name: Oh, okay. Sure. I hope you make it back safe.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1049
rows.name:
Sorry, I was just...kinda...spacing out there.
Do you have a new mission for me?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1050
rows.name: Okay. Thanks. I'll try not to slow you down.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1051
rows.name:
Okay. If you ever change your mind, I'll be ready.
Well, to the extent that I'll ever be, at least.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1056
rows.name: I guess we should be chasing after Lao at this point.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1057
rows.name:
I'll try to help out however I can, so don't hesitate to
take me with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1058
rows.name:
Okay, that's good. We should, uh...
We should probably hurry.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1059
rows.name:
Okay. If you ever change your mind, I'll be ready.
Well, to the extent that I'll ever be, at least.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1066
rows.name:
Okay, I'm ready to go. And kind of eager, even!
I mean, I am if you are. And if you want me to be?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1067
rows.name:
My life's on the line here, too—and I want to be the
one to save it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1068
rows.name:
Sure, of course. I totally understand.
I'll be here praying for your success.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1073
rows.name: Isn't it nice to be at peace?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1074
rows.name:
Everyone in the residential district looks like they're
positively floating...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1075
rows.name:
I want to keep it this way. And if that means having to
fight a little bit more, then I'm willing to do it!
So what do you say?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1076
rows.name:
Really? Wow, that's great! So to be honest,
I'm a terrible fighter—but I'll work really hard.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1077
rows.name:
Yeah, okay. I'll be here if you change your mind.
I've got a lot to think about in the meantime.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1078
rows.name: Oh, um... Yeah, sorry, but I'm kind of busy right now.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev001001_MSG1079
rows.name: Maybe we could do this some other time?[ST:wait ]
